nodes.title: Stuff I randomly tried before
widgets_values:
Best for starters:

double_blocks\.([5-7]|1[2-6])\.txt_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.5
single_blocks\.([1-5])\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=0.5


Default:

double_blocks\.([0-9]+)\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.1
single_blocks\.([0-9]+)\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=1.1


Emphasize the Early Blocks

double_blocks\.([0-5])\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.5
single_blocks\.([0-5])\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=1.5


Reduce Influence on Later Blocks

double_blocks\.(3[0-7]|2[5-9])\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.7
single_blocks\.(3[0-7]|2[5-9])\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=0.7


Enhance Specific Components within Middle Blocks


double_blocks\.1[0-7]\.(img|txt)_attn\.(qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.3
single_blocks\.1[0-7]\.linear2\.(weight|bias)=1.3


Alternate Enhancements in Odd-Indexed Blocks


double_blocks\.(2[8-9]|3[0-7])\.(img|txt)_mlp\.[02]\.(lin|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.4
single_blocks\.(2[8-9]|3[0-7])\.modulation\.lin\.(weight|bias)=1.4


Increase Focus on Attention Projections Across the Entire Model (not a good idea, lol)


double_blocks\.([0-9]|[1-3][0-7])\.(img|txt)_attn\.(proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.6
single_blocks\.([0-9]|[1-3][0-7])\.linear2\.(weight|bias)=1.6


Gradual Decrease in Scaling Factors Through the Model

double_blocks\.([0-9])\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.4
double_blocks\.1[0-9]\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.2
double_blocks\.2[0-9]\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|proj)\.(weight|bias)=1.0
double_blocks\.3[0-7]\.(img|txt)_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.8

single_blocks\.([0-9])\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=1.4
single_blocks\.1[0-9]\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=1.2
single_blocks\.2[0-9]\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=1.0
single_blocks\.3[0-7]\.(linear[12]|modulation\.lin)\.(weight|bias)=0.8



Dropping Text Influence in Later Blocks for single_blocks (it's all going downhill from here!)

single_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.linear2\.(weight|bias)=0.0
single_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.modulation\.lin\.(weight|bias)=0.0


Dropping Text Influence in Later Blocks for double_blocks (don't do that, flux needs a text)

double_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.txt_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.0


Dropping Text Influence in Later Blocks for Both single_blocks and double_blocks (it's a bad idea, really)

single_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.linear2\.(weight|bias)=0.0
single_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.modulation\.lin\.(weight|bias)=0.0

double_blocks\.(2[5-9]|3[0-7])\.txt_(mod|attn|mlp\.[02])\.(lin|qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.0


Dump text in intermediate layers only, single_blocks (all of that ruins it, srsly):

single_blocks\.(1[0-9])\.linear2\.(weight|bias)=0.0
single_blocks\.(1[0-9])\.modulation\.lin\.(weight|bias)=0.0


Lower text attention (zero is absolutely destructive!)

single_blocks\.(1[0-9])\.txt_attn\.(qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.05
double_blocks\.(1[1-6])\.txt_attn\.(qkv|proj)\.(weight|bias)=0.0
